com.yworks.yfiles.view.Mouse2DEvent

  • Packages that use Mouse2DEvent 
    Package Description
    com.yworks.yfiles.view
    Contains the main UI classes, interfaces, default implementations and support classes that can be used to display IGraph instances.

      A mouse click has been recognized.

      static EventType<Mouse2DEvent> Mouse2DEvent.RELEASED
      A button has been released.
      static EventType<Mouse2DEvent> Mouse2DEvent.WHEEL_TURNED
      The mouse wheel has been turned.
